snippet.title: 0. Full-stack Army - Welcome | Decision-Making Video | Complete MERN Stack Journey in Bangla
snippet.description:
Full-stack Army - Welcome
With this video, we are going to start our journey as a full-stack / MERN stack developer. This is going to be the most advanced MERN stack series freely available on youtube. No videos in this series will be recorded, you will get recordings of our live classes. In this video, we have just discussed why we decide to go with the full-stack army course.
